{"tid":714863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北辰：據消息透露紅磡站月台被剪短鋼筋達5000支","createTime":"2018-06-24T03:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T08:30:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a35ffbe5d26333909dd2f7a671092639be95a278","tid":714863,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1403319-20180624.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1403319-20180624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qGEn258Ii1sbyQSJeHwt0ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=03383aa5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1403319-20180624.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f0f395d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1403319-20180624.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會主席田北辰說，有消息向他透露，沙中綫紅磡站月台及連續牆銜接位的26000支鋼筋中，有多達兩成，即是多達5000支鋼筋被人剪短，未有扭入螺絲帽。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰表示，擔心港鐵委託的專家只進行壓力測試，看不到長遠問題，提出拆除月台5幅牆的部分石屎，檢查當中的鋼筋。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰說，既然他聽到有關消息，應做到「小心駛得萬年船」，因此提出檢查有關5幅連續牆內鋼筋，他已尋求專家意見，認為並非很大工程。"},{"pid":"8d7c8d3d5f3e0f98b5d3c496b08d24b0f94d4215","tid":714863,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:03:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e35f0b3183b5c5bd1033d7c4130a6abdcdf08a04","tid":714863,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"元朗都沉降照行，未死人無事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb7b2171a2f51c5e603d946430e56bc3c04ae93","tid":714863,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:18:41.000Z","msg":"港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731183f536a3a5b883d113cd71f7f21e59586eb4","tid":714863,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T07:20:04.00